PART 7Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äî ROLLING BACK MIGRATIONS
php artisan migrate:rollback     // last batch
php artisan migrate:reset        // all migrations
php artisan migrate:refresh      // rollback + migrate
php artisan migrate:fresh        // drop all tables + migrate
